      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "One of the things to do at the Baths is taste the \"healing\" water from the Baths themselves. I took one sip, but it was definitely not a pleasant water-drinking experience. :)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
