      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "And finally, before catching the train back to Bristol, we went to "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Pulteney Arms"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", a local pub, to try to grab dinner. The kitchen ended up being closed, so we just ordered a couple of drinks instead. Even though we didn't get to try the food, I still recommend the pub because it was off-the-beaten-path, cozy, and full of locals."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
